name: Intense Encounters
description: Our hero finaly makes contact with the locals, albeit under the influence of toxic spores that made their way into our explorer's air supply, giving surreal overtones to this historic moment. This is the second chapter in an exploratory adventure series of lens based cinemagraphs shot on location in the andean region of Quebrada de las Señoritas, a follow up to the 1/1 piece "NIGHTFALL".
